One More Thing I Noticed:-

You commented out live links:
// live: "https://..."

So your Live Demo button may open undefined.
To fix safely:

{project.live && (
  <a
    href={project.live}
    target="_blank"
    className="bg-black text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-lg"
  >
    Live Demo
  </a>
)}

Now button only appears if a live link exists.